data.description: Step into this spacious 2,000 square foot haven, boasting 5 inviting bedrooms, 2 full baths, and a bonus room brimming with endless possibilities. Whether you're seeking space for your growing family or envisioning new beginnings, this home has room for it all! As you ascend the stairs, discover a tranquil retreat with 3 bedrooms, a cozy living area, and a well-appointed kitchen, perfect for whipping up delicious meals and creating memories. Descend downstairs to find 2 additional bedrooms, a full bath, laundry facilities, and that versatile bonus room awaiting your personal touch. Inside, indulge in the comforts of modern living with fresh flooring in carpet, hardwood, and tile, complemented by new paint and fixtures throughout. And with recent upgrades to the roof, windows, and HVAC system in 2017, peace of mind is yours to enjoy. But the real magic awaits outside in your expansive backyard oasis, complete with a new privacy fence built in 2020, offering the perfect backdrop for weekend BBQs and outdoor gatherings. Dive into relaxation with a refreshing pool, unwind by the fire pit, or start your own garden adventure with a raised garden bed.
